data.description: Coastal Gem with Intracoastal Views. Welcome to your new home in paradise! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven is perfectly nestled along the Intracoastal Waterway, offering both coastal tranquility and city conveniences. Step inside to discover an open floor plan. The kitchen is expansive with plenty of cabinets, inviting wood-look flooring that complements the coastal vibe and is both stylish and easy to maintain.  Tranquil evenings on the 12x34 screened porch, conveniently located on the East side of the home. Nestled in the heart of Gulf Shores, you'll be only a few blocks away from the upcoming Waterway Village, featuring Acme Oyster House, Beach Brewery, Tacky Jacks, and more. This exciting downtown district is on the cusp of becoming a bustling hub for entertainment and dining. Looking for Proximity to sandy shores and turquoise waters? You're just a stone's throw away from the glorious beaches of the Gulf of Mexico. Spend your weekends sunbathing, swimming, and building memories with loved ones. n addition to the beach, you're within minutes of The Wharf, Owa Amusement Park, outlet malls, diverse dining options, theaters, and a vibrant nightlife. Your days and nights will be filled with endless entertainment. Meyer Park is a short walk away, offering music, sports, movies, and a great space to connect with nature. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this coastal gem your own. Whether you're seeking a serene retreat or a hub for coastal living, this home has it all. Homes in this desirable location are in high demand.
